    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Envisioning Your Future\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Interact with the chatbot by uploading a picture of your vision board.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat how you might incorporate emerging technology into a future career.\r\n  \r\nTry this prompt:\r\n> Look at my Careers in Technology vision board and suggest some emerging technologies that I might use.\r\n\r\n**Tip:** You can also provide the career and ask what emerging technology might be used with that career.\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Device**\r\n- Then browse your local files.\r\n- When you find your vision board, click it to select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need to download your vision board?**]\r\nClick **File** -> **Download** -> **PNG image**\r\n![](https://images.code.org/9225f6b1e5062f6a5aac87ff9e8d2dbc-image-1745347859241.50.50 PM.png)\r\n:::",
